<p><strong>Anabasis</strong> I've been waiting here for what now seems the better of an hour</p>
<p><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/SCP-2084">Start here</a></p>
<p><strong>Author:</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/andarielhalo" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1750255); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1750255&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721460" alt="AndarielHalo" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1750255)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/andarielhalo" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1750255); return false;">AndarielHalo</a></span></p>
